rentzian-like functions and a Gaussian. Our analysis\nclearly illustrates the need for a more sophisticated granulation model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Jan 2011 14:34:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
